{"tid":1963614,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【韓國實測】確診者咳嗽外科口罩難完全阻擋飛沫　何栢良：病人口罩外應加面罩","createTime":"2020-04-08T09:03:43.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-09T07:26:33.000Z","uid":1886,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"fefaee4443da4d862d9eecebd9cb2a46fbb91ecd","tid":1963614,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-08T09:03:43.000Z","msg":"中國武漢肺炎疫情持續，口罩成為日常防疫必備品，但有最新醫學研究指出，無論是醫用外科口罩（Surgical Mask）或布口罩（Cotton Mask），都無法有效過濾病毒。研究團隊以確診者進行試驗，透過患者咳嗽來測試口罩防疫功能，結果發現未能完全阻擋飛沫噴出 。港大傳染病中心總監何栢良表示，口罩只能阻隔部分微細飛沫是預期之內，建議確診者求醫時應在口罩上外加面罩。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://static02-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2610000/2613292/92608400_1174153479643409_5692343332479434752_n_600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic02-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2610000%2F2613292%2F92608400_1174153479643409_5692343332479434752_n_600.jpg&h=871ce1b5&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://topick.hket.com/article/2613292/【韓國實測】確診者咳嗽外科口罩難完全阻擋飛沫%E3%80%80何栢良：病人口罩外應加面罩\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2613292%2F%E3%80%90%E9%9F%93%E5%9C%8B%E5%AF%A6%E6%B8%AC%E3%80%91%E7%A2%BA%E8%A8%BA%E8%80%85%E5%92%B3%E5%97%BD%E5%A4%96%E7%A7%91%E5%8F%A3%E7%BD%A9%E9%9B%A3%E5%AE%8C%E5%85%A8%E9%98%BB%E6%93%8B%E9%A3%9B%E6%B2%AB%25E3%2580%2580%E4%BD%95%E6%A0%A2%E8%89%AF%EF%BC%9A%E7%97%85%E4%BA%BA%E5%8F%A3%E7%BD%A9%E5%A4%96%E6%87%89%E5%8A%A0%E9%9D%A2%E7%BD%A9&d=LgTIxyFtuo0acoW68XVTBYkJ8G0wCzjK2GZdEgWvKr0%3D&h=1e750c83\" target=\"_blank\">https://topick.hket.com/article/2613292/【韓國實測】確診者咳嗽外科口罩難完全阻擋飛沫%E3%80%80何栢良：病人口罩外應加面罩</a>"},{"pid":"bad42c3e4bd14233530845f4e4ac72f2759ffa4b","tid":1963614,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-08T09:04:52.000Z","msg":"相關研究由韓國蔚山大學醫學院，聯合中央大學醫院進行，而研究結果已於美國醫學期刊《Annals of Internal Medicine》上刊出。研究人員安排4名確診者咳嗽5次，再在距離病人18厘米的地方放置收集皿，採集樣本。<br />\n<br />\n結果發現，在患者佩戴的口罩外層，比內層更受污染，口罩無法完全過濾病毒。病毒可穿透口罩外層，散布四周。然而，實驗範圍僅限外科口罩及布口罩，未有同時測試N95口罩。而研究亦未說明，病毒外漏與「患者咳嗽力道大小」或「病毒顆粒大小」相關與否。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://annals.org/aim/fullarticle/2764367/effectiveness-surgical-cotton-masks-blocking-sars-cov-2-controlled-comparison\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fannals.org%2Faim%2Ffullarticle%2F2764367%2Feffectiveness-surgical-cotton-masks-blocking-sars-cov-2-controlled-comparison&d=LgTIxyFtuo0acoW68XVTBYkJ8G0wCzjK2GZdEgWvKr0%3D&h=cf5d0eb3\" target=\"_blank\">https://annals.org/aim/fullarticle/2764367/effectiveness-surgical-cotton-masks-blocking-sars-cov-2-controlled-comparison</a>"},{"pid":"24fd3df44f95fdea5a184456a5328f79d62c6968","tid":1963614,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-08T09:06:43.000Z","msg":"何栢良在Facebook表示，美國麻省理工學院（MIT）一項研究曾指出，病人咳嗽的時候，飛沫氣流研究顯示噴出的飛沫時速可達100公里，所以口罩只能夠阻隔部分超跑速度的微細飛沫，是預期之內。<br />\n<br />\nMIT有研究指出，咳嗽或打噴嚏噴出的飛沫，能以每秒10至30米的速度傳播，最遠可跨越7至8米，因此人與人間可能要相隔8米，才能防止病毒傳播。相關報道見：<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://topick.hket.com/article/2605848/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2605848%2F&d=LgTIxyFtuo0acoW68XVTBYkJ8G0wCzjK2GZdEgWvKr0%3D&h=5ef8c955\" target=\"_blank\">https://topick.hket.com/article/2605848/</a>"},{"pid":"ba8128ad3817062288e92b5d0b7c5ff708643116","tid":1963614,"uid":36901,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-08T09:06:54.000Z","msg":"個測試應該要計埋有戴罩同冇戴罩個social distance 分別"},{"pid":"f3e20c775392ac436b08682a21e2dcbf3f712c88","tid":1963614,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-08T09:07:05.000Z","msg":"何栢良表示，有病徵例如咳嗽的病人，前往求診時必須佩戴外科口罩，加強源頭控制。而確診病人住院期間，在醫護人員接近的時候，病人亦應在載上口罩時，再外加配戴面罩。"},{"pid":"ab3e1a8da239765371d781d1606258fb993a7ab0","tid":1963614,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T02:43:45.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: green;\"></span>"},{"pid":"efe6e07d180ae8df04a42b01971bbfe77677c956","tid":1963614,"uid":131157,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T02:48:02.000Z","msg":"呢條友愈玩愈大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ea679568ebf9e517ee665ce7f3926086814fa88","tid":1963614,"uid":9726,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T04:49:17.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6b92e3e9456998730e0cde2e92a6bf6e04948cd7","tid":1963614,"uid":194130,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T07:04:36.000Z","msg":"個測試只係證明左<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">只有病人載口罩</span></span>係冇用<br />\n佢個結果係未能完全阻擋,唔係完全未能阻擋<br />\n就算LV3都係99%點都唔係100%架啦<br />\n再加上咳得大力會推開口罩邊出風<br />\n病人載左阻大部分<br />\n其他人再載阻埋其他部分先有用<br />\n所以一般人都要載口罩黎保護自己"},{"pid":"aaa877e035588062b013bd3cee509aef968cfcf3","tid":1963614,"uid":42687,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T07:07:35.000Z","msg":"其實香港人一早知係隔唔哂啦駛撚你講，但隔到幾多得幾多盡做者。<br />\n夠薑你英美澳加韓日醫護人員唔好戴出街又唔戴齊齊攬炒囉。"},{"pid":"e02fc7d60d51eea4fb0d11f036539be23a37edbf","tid":1963614,"uid":50088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T07:08:50.000Z","msg":"樓主麻煩pin我<br />\n呢單嘢完全係班韓仔計錯數<br />\n篇paper完全唔識計log<br />\n你睇返d stat其實布口罩減少細菌量達9成<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而且d method奇奇怪怪<br />\npatient cough左幾次但口罩入面驗唔到有菌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d89572a8b74675c946e234354442119c430b5acd","tid":1963614,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6b92e3e9456998730e0cde2e92a6bf6e04948cd7","tid":1963614,"uid":194130,"like":1,"dislike":0